Create KPI Visualization 9

Arrest Rate KPI and Crime Rate KPI

Select KPI visual

Go to the Fields pane

Drag and drop CrimeRate on the Indicator

Drag and drop Year on the Trend axis

Drag and drop CrimeRateTarget on the Target goals

Go to the Format pane, select color code and select low is good.



Repeat the same steps for ArrestRate by dragging and dropping the following in the Field pane

ArrestRate  in the Indicator 

Year in Trend the axis 

ArrestRateTarget in the Target goals 

Go to the Format pane, select color code and select High is good.
